Selenium Class 10

How ta handle Calendars:
1. Click on the calendar
2. Locate the month and get the text
3. If the desired text is not visible --> we will keep clicking on next and kee updating the text of the month
4. As soon we found our desired month --> grab all the cells from the table and put them into List
5. Loop through the cells
6. Once the cell value is matched with our condition --> click on the matched date

Why do we need screenshots in testing
- In testing it is very important to take screenshot in order to us to prove that our test case
covered certain functionality-

In Selenium in order to take screenshots we will be using TakesScreenshot interface


Actions class:
Is given by Selenium to capture keyboard and mouse events such as:
move to element
drag and drop
double click
right click

